gui.arena.tip.full_bag_drop=§eDiscard full backpack§r\n§7When the backpack is completely full, \n§7 will automatically discard items with the lowest value according to the priority you set, \n§7 to make room for high-value items that may appear \n§7.
gui.arena.tip.priority_settings=§eDiscard priority setting§r\n§7 is used to configure the order of item discarding when the backpack is full. \n§7 This button is always displayed to facilitate editing the priority in advance.
gui.arena.tip.item_top=§e Item on top§r\n§7 When enabled, the specified item \n§7 (see the input box on the right) will be automatically moved to the first grid of the \n§7 shortcut bar.
gui.arena.tip.pickup_settings=§e Taking Settings §r\n§7 Configure the \n§7 speed, delay and batch mode for taking items from the box, \n§7 to adapt to different network environments.
gui.arena.tip.drop_settings=§e Discard Settings §r\n§7 Configure advanced parameters such as \n§7 speed, frequency and batch operation mode of item handling, \n§7 to adapt to different network environments.
gui.arena.tip.auto_evac=After §e automatic evacuation §r\n§7 is enabled, when any condition of \n§7 configured on the right is met (such as the backpack is full, an item is obtained), the \n§7 script will automatically stop and execute the evacuation sequence.
gui.arena.tip.reset_protection=§eReset protection status§r\n§7If an item fails to be discarded continuously due to server plug-ins and other reasons \n§7, the Mod will suspend processing it. \n§7 Click this button to clear the paused status of all items, \n§7 retry processing immediately.
gui.arena.tip.add_current_inventory=§e Add the current backpack with one click §r\n§7 Quickly scan your main backpack \n§7 (excluding the shortcut bar and equipment bar), \n§7 and add all the items in it to the \n§7 custom list below.
